    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Awaken Infinity</strong> is a visual novel with top-down 2D segments. You wake up with no memory in a locked, futuristic room, and the only one you can talk to is an artificial intelligence. Will you uncover the truth?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/5bbfd6a8aabaf3ad264f16a274ae4206.poster.avif?t=1759478080\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/5bbfd6a8aabaf3ad264f16a274ae4206.webm?t=1759478080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/5bbfd6a8aabaf3ad264f16a274ae4206.mp4?t=1759478080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What is it?</strong><br>Awaken Infinity is a compact, story-driven experience that blends visual novel storytelling with a touch of top-down 2D exploration. It’s designed to be completed in a single sitting—focused and without filler. Illustrated scenes and dialogue drive the narrative, while short top-down 2D segments enhance the story without overshadowing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/7dd1f7e3628ce98f4197a644f88cec20.poster.avif?t=1759478080\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/7dd1f7e3628ce98f4197a644f88cec20.webm?t=1759478080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168400/extras/7dd1f7e3628ce98f4197a644f88cec20.mp4?t=1759478080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What you’ll do</strong><br>• Wake up with no memory and try to make sense of your situation in a sterile, futuristic environment.<br>• Make choices that influence dialogue, unlock optional lines, and reveal short extra scenes.<br>• Explore in short top-down 2D segments to examine objects, trigger events, and uncover clues that deepen the narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
